room_title: Escape room "Murder Mystery on Baker Street" by Escape on Main in St. Louis
room_address: 340 North Main Street Ste 205 Saint Charles, MO 63301
room_description:
You have been directed to the Baker Street Five hideout so you may solve the murder and end their crime spree once and for all.

An informant has turned on the gang and has left subtle hints and clues for you, as well as a means of escape from the building.

One word of warning, the leader of the Baker Street Five is leaving the country within the next hour, so you had better work quickly.
